      "text": [
        " «مِنْ ذَلِكَ اَلتَّمَشُّطُ عِنْدَ كُلِّ صَلاَةٍ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.318 - Abu Al-Hasan Imam Ali ibn Musa Ar-Ridha (as) was asked about the saying of Allah (swt), the Mighty and Glorious:\n'Take your adornment at every place of worship.' (Surah Al-A’raf 7:31).\nImam (as) said: \"Part of that includes combing one's hair before every prayer”."
        ]
      }
